{"tid":2205860,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【立場新聞哲學版】一眾哲學老師教你 讀哲學嘅要訣","createTime":"2020-09-17T06:03:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T04:15:04.000Z","uid":138409,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3f278507d2ea72747e05eef9a9e5ec7d813eec26","tid":2205860,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T06:03:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.thestandnews.com/philosophy/%E5%93%B2%E5%AD%B8%E8%A6%81%E8%A8%A3/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fphilosophy%2F%25E5%2593%25B2%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%25A8%25A3%2F&d=WBhgCLuhUD%2FUeH80S3I9%2BvZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=6a03aaaf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fphilosophy%2F%25E5%2593%25B2%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%25A8%25A3%2F&h=9415372a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.thestandnews.com/philosophy/%E5%93%B2%E5%AD%B8%E8%A6%81%E8%A8%A3/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"xx-large\">tl;dr</span></span><br />\n<br />\n- <span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">學好英文</span></span><br />\n- 睇多啲哲學以外嘅書：心理學、歷史、自然科學、統計學 etc<br />\n- 睇書嘅時候要有耐性，同情地了解作者嘅想法，並且關心相關思想對哲學議題嘅應用，唔好為讀而讀。<br />\n- 睇書要確保自己能夠清晰解釋本書講左啲乜；寫筆記，同其他人討論下<br />\n- 追隨自己嘅興趣，有自己關心嘅議題<br />\n- 虛心思考他人嘅批評"},{"pid":"c40707681639007f609420cbbcf9c3f3f7d3e71e","tid":2205860,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T06:04:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"92bf8e415fc024badc7c3b975680b8b95bbc4992","tid":2205860,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T06:06:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d1e16bd7be7d0411bf1122e55c08de590af5b8f4","tid":2205860,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T06:07:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d480bdae6eaff832940712668704d16508a39aa9","tid":2205860,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T06:08:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e493fe06fdae536c8dada097c8e36f7963497f9c","tid":2205860,"uid":34553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T06:42:55.000Z","msg":"寫筆記<br />\n我真係好懶"},{"pid":"0436f03f5b1145c581ddd94a25771b10f68f1f9d","tid":2205860,"uid":84511,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T07:09:00.000Z","msg":"當你見到立場搵到嘅作者<br />\n個個都有幾分名氣<br />\n而且仲要好多都係華人學圈做緊prof.<br />\n華人學圈好緊繃 呢啲人通常都好忙好忙<br />\n但竟然都肯抽時間幫立場寫文<br />\n就知佢地放幾多心力係學圈以外嘅哲普工作<br />\n完全體會到：<br />\n「我地身處最壞嘅時代；<br />\n我地身處最好嘅時代。」"},{"pid":"a7665f6ba76bee18944b0bb48f536bb606061b5f","tid":2205860,"uid":138409,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"0436f03f5b1145c581ddd94a25771b10f68f1f9d","tid":2205860,"uid":84511,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T07:09:00.000Z","msg":"當你見到立場搵到嘅作者<br />\n個個都有幾分名氣<br />\n而且仲要好多都係華人學圈做緊prof.<br />\n華人學圈好緊繃 呢啲人通常都好忙好忙<br />\n但竟然都肯抽時間幫立場寫文<br />\n就知佢地放幾多心力係學圈以外嘅哲普工作<br />\n完全體會到：<br />\n「我地身處最壞嘅時代；<br />\n我地身處最好嘅時代。」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T11:25:57.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n而且幫立場寫文響職業上對佢地無額外好處<br />\n真係為興趣 / 愛"},{"pid":"5746e381a1e92ba3edbd0a708d550360363289fe","tid":2205860,"uid":259812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T11:29:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15beb713c4ba3353ee89a49ad4b52a81f0e21563","tid":2205860,"uid":55493,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T11:33:45.000Z","msg":"阿劉生<br />\n二、不要神化（大）哲學家，但更加要小心中二病。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真呀，好多網上哲學討論係覺得躂個哲學家名出嚟話佢講過咩咩咩就當解咗條題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35c6cd56f7e9bda07b630f3cbfc47afc4cacec61","tid":2205860,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15beb713c4ba3353ee89a49ad4b52a81f0e21563","tid":2205860,"uid":55493,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T11:33:45.000Z","msg":"阿劉生<br />\n二、不要神化（大）哲學家，但更加要小心中二病。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真呀，好多網上哲學討論係覺得躂個哲學家名出嚟話佢講過咩咩咩就當解咗條題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T11:52:35.000Z","msg":"睇呢篇文嗰陣見到呢句都笑左出聲<br />\n好傳神<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00eb1cbd63efb591d1adeea251d4d0f8aa7548f7","tid":2205860,"uid":136590,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T16:57:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>六、找志趣相投的人一起讀和討論，你說不清的東西等於你還不明白。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢點好重要<br />\n因為討論嘅時候要用返自己嘅語言去整合觀點<br />\n呢個時候就好容易發現自己係咪真係睇得明本書<br />\n加上每個人都一定會讀到唔同嘅嘢<br />\n大家一齊砌返個full picture出嚟會讀快好多<br />\n<br />\n同埋讀哲學最正嘅位往往係思辨嘅過程<br />\n而同人討論就係最好嘅思辨<br />\n學維根斯坦話齋<br />\n一個唔參與討論嘅哲學家，就好似一個從來唔上台比賽嘅拳手一樣"},{"pid":"3f15d8ca128e0543350a1a80c8ee572b83b1f80e","tid":2205860,"uid":244357,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T04:18:38.000Z","msg":"Thanks for sharing<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過對於唔係做哲學既大多數人，點樣係工餘時間維持對哲學既興趣或者更重要。"},{"pid":"35f27f90cfc97c02403f89477053e81c5ada3453","tid":2205860,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f15d8ca128e0543350a1a80c8ee572b83b1f80e","tid":2205860,"uid":244357,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T04:18:38.000Z","msg":"Thanks for sharing<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過對於唔係做哲學既大多數人，點樣係工餘時間維持對哲學既興趣或者更重要。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T05:05:15.000Z","msg":"咁呢個當然<br />\n首先要有興趣先"},{"pid":"52dc99a66f01819b92d41292968523130a235e99","tid":2205860,"uid":244357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35f27f90cfc97c02403f89477053e81c5ada3453","tid":2205860,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f15d8ca128e0543350a1a80c8ee572b83b1f80e","tid":2205860,"uid":244357,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,